description: Welcome to spelling bee, the very first spelling game on Alexa. There are several hundred words, so every time you play, it's a fresh, new challenge. Currently, the words are at a 5th grade level. If you have ideas about how to make this skill more awesome, let me know! All feedback is welcome.
